metadata.name: White Ox(White Bull) by Korean Painter Lee Jung Seob
metadata.description: White Ox(White Bull) is arguablly the most well known Korean artist Lee Jung Seob's work and it is generally accepted there are five known versions of 'Ox' or 'Bull' paintings.  The Ox was the subject of paintings throughout his life. His 'Ox' series can be characterized by his use of bold lines, making the animal look powerful.
